OL,3,CNew Government fund aims to support
OL,4,Cstruggling families
OL,6,FVulnerable children and families
OL,7,Facross the North West could benefit
OL,8,Ffrom a new government fund.
OL,10,FThe Better Futures Fund, launched by
OL,11,FChancellor Rachel Reeves during a
OL,12,Fvisit to a school in Wigan, aims to
OL,13,Fhelp up to 200,000 children and
OL,14,Ffamilies across the country over the
OL,15,Fnext ten years.
OL,17,FThe fund is designed to bring together
OL,18,Flocal councils, charities, social
OL,19,Fenterprises and community groups to
OL,20,Fprovide early support to children
OL,21,Ffacing disadvantage.
