OL,3,CNew Government fund aims to support
OL,4,Cstruggling families
OL,6,FThat could include support in schools
OL,7,Fto boost attendance and behaviour,
OL,8,Fhelp for young people at risk of crime
OL,9,Fand employment support to secure
OL,10,Fbrighter futures.
OL,12,FWigan-based charity AllChild, which
OL,13,Fhosted the launch, has already seen
OL,14,Fsuccess with local projects, reporting
OL,15,Fa reduction in persistent school
OL,16,Fabsence and improvements in children's
OL,17,Fwellbeing.
