OL,3,CNew Government fund aims to support
OL,4,Cstruggling families
OL,6,FLouisa Mitchell MBE, Chief Executive
OL,7,Fof AllChild, said: "I warmly welcome
OL,8,Fthe government's Better Futures Fund
OL,9,Fas a pivotal step toward transforming
OL,10,Fhow we support children and families
OL,11,Facross the country.
OL,13,F"It's vital that children engage with
OL,14,Fthe right support and opportunities,
OL,15,Fat the right time, in the right way."
