OL,3,CNew Government fund aims to support
OL,4,Cstruggling families
OL,6,FThe government says the fund, which is
OL,7,Fthe largest of its kind globally,
OL,8,Fforms part of a wider Plan for Change
OL,9,Fto give every child a safe home,
OL,10,Faccess to education, and opportunities
OL,11,Fto succeed.
OL,13,FBut some in the region are urging
OL,14,Fcaution. Community organisations say
OL,15,Fthat while the fund is welcome, it
OL,16,Fmust be matched with long-term
OL,17,Finvestment and practical support for
OL,18,Foverstretched local services.
