OL,3,CNew Government fund aims to support
OL,4,Cstruggling families
OL,6,FGreater Manchester has already seen
OL,7,Fsocial outcomes partnerships in
OL,8,Faction, including programmes to help
OL,9,Fyoung people avoid homelessness and
OL,10,Freoffending. Local leaders say
OL,11,Fcontinued support will be crucial to
OL,12,Fexpand those efforts.
OL,14,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said: "This
OL,15,Ffund will give hundreds of thousands
OL,16,Fof children, young people and their
OL,17,Ffamilies a better chance.
