OL,3,CNew Government fund aims to support
OL,4,Cstruggling families
OL,6,F"For too long, these children have
OL,7,Fbeen overlooked. Our Plan for Change
OL,8,Fwill break down barriers to
OL,9,Fopportunity and give them the best
OL,10,Fstart in life."
OL,12,FFurther details of how the Better
OL,13,FFutures Fund will be rolled out in the
OL,14,FNorth West are expected later this
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FIt comes as the government prepares to
OL,18,Fpublish a Child Poverty Strategy in
OL,19,Fthe autumn, setting out plans to
OL,20,Faddress long-standing inequalities
OL,21,Facross the UK.
